    <item>
      <title>圣诞节前后美元将达到峰值：法国兴业银行的 Juckes</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/peak-dollar-coming-around-christmas-socgen-s-juckes-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国兴业银行首席外汇策略师基特·朱克斯 (Kit Juckes) 表示，美元“肯定会进一步上涨”，他预计美元将在今年年底前达到峰值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-12/peak-dollar-coming-around-christmas-socgen-s-juckes-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 12:18:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>热爱埃隆·马斯克的日内交易者正在席卷投机市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/musk-investment-complex-takes-off-in-market-s-riskiest-pockets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊隆·马斯克的日内交易粉丝俱乐部正在疯狂购买市场上一些最具投机性的领域，从搞笑的加密货币狗狗币到将 SpaceX 视为其主要持股的备受争议的封闭式基金 — 所有这些都是为了希望唐纳德·特朗普的当选能释放更多的动物精神。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/musk-investment-complex-takes-off-in-market-s-riskiest-pockets</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 12:17:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔选择卡塔尔投资局美洲区负责人管理 5100 亿美元基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/qatar-names-mohammed-al-suwaidi-head-of-500-billion-wealth-fund</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔任命穆罕默德·阿尔索瓦迪 (Mohammed Al Sowaidi) 为其 5100 亿美元主权财富基金的首席执行官，该基金将在未来几年获得更强大的金融实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/qatar-names-mohammed-al-suwaidi-head-of-500-billion-wealth-fund</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:27:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行将加强对银行地缘政治风险的关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/ecb-is-set-to-step-up-focus-on-geopolitical-risks-at-banks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行监管负责人克劳迪娅·布赫 (Claudia Buch) 已开始对该机构施加影响，欧洲央行计划要求银行提供更多有关其地缘政治风险敞口的信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/ecb-is-set-to-step-up-focus-on-geopolitical-risks-at-banks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 11:05:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
